        "message": "LU-19248 tests: Wait for fake intf ipv6 dup detection\n\nIPv6 addresses undergo duplicate address detection during which they\nare flagged as \"tentative\" in the output of ip addr show. Some test\ncases do not work correctly until this flag is cleared on the fake\ninterface that is created in setup_fakeif(). Modify this function to\nwait for the flag to be cleared before returning.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Chris Horn <chris.horn@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: Ie7217feb7ed3c407f66f3d4a48fbb954870dd521\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/60677\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Frank Sehr <fsehr@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Serguei Smirnov <ssmirnov@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
